{"tid":338983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日覺得自己好冇用","createTime":"2017-07-28T16:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T16:51:06.000Z","uid":124514,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"290f438cd7ae645858151a966a02460488aff619","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得自己好冇用，自問返工做野都幾用心，奈何唔醒目記性又差，所以做野好騰雞，又俾人話唔上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好灰心，但我真係有努力過，我覺得自己咩都做唔黎咁，無論係讀書定返工都係個失敗者，我有諗過係因為自己自卑先影響到工作能力，因為成日睇死自己做唔到，但係我又控制唔到咁諗，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁廢"},{"pid":"2b3b039463782a02aa2ec4b4d5783992f6d08843","tid":338983,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"好似講緊自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd545933bde245882a7a8b097a427d38b6230ef","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似講緊自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打同病相憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aefed20a8913c7f29f9447bab26c5da4ef79e7","tid":338983,"uid":114015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:16:49.000Z","msg":"咩工咁大壓力"},{"pid":"d6934ed4d29ac1ef901c8ed62be4ec5543a1a27b","tid":338983,"uid":90945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"中曬，已經覺得自己好努力，但係努力耐左都會心攰，心有餘而力不足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff4506aa9b8e2d18c4d0a255646f92b24a382c4","tid":338983,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同我一樣 成日變得好負面 想死"},{"pid":"a85edeaf22a01f4d32e595f1c939ed8c98b78dfe","tid":338983,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci