src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有工返但係返唔長呢。。。好咩好"},{"pid":"2e239324cf7bfce6a0507f286102ee0f0e6bb076","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有工反都幾好丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有工返但係返唔長呢。。。有咩好</blockquote>"},{"pid":"dd5e6d6b23f620f0736336f8e7d2f8c734515275","tid":338983,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a23afd7347cbabccaf69c5ed7b207c2d825979","tid":338983,"uid":114015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩工咁大壓力</blockquote><br />\n見暑假咩工都去試下，去做收銀結果覺得壓力好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚找錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暑期工唔啱做咪走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079c0aec201736274210a83434e49a3a62e4a29d","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩工咁大壓力</blockquote><br />\n見暑假咩工都去試下，去做收銀結果覺得壓力好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚找錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暑期工唔啱做咪走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係姐。。。只係覺得自己好無用。。。咩都做唔黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b9dd6675b7d52c52e8d4afdb065f0ad6f4e012","tid":338983,"uid":71864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"我都係。成日諗野好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b80370bdf04a24d50bd72e1f34ac7db032a42b","tid":338983,"uid":60689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩工咁大壓力</blockquote><br />\n見暑假咩工都去試下，去做收銀結果覺得壓力好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚找錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暑期工唔啱做咪走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係姐。。。只係覺得自己好無用。。。咩都做唔黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係做緊收銀,次次數錢都會check好多次,但都係覺得自己會錯，連數錢咁簡單都睇死自己，又試過check得太多次比個客屌"},{"pid":"47d81077fb65a8df97e62dfcbfbea1c84391e7ba","tid":338983,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:16:50.000Z","msg":"係 性格又怕麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63d5adc7fef863ff21ac0c9183df45ea4845868","tid":338983,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:22:31.000Z","msg":"以前諗野好正面 最後被學業 現實 搞到好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書又唔叻 學歷又唔好 體能岩岩先起步操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要係自己連夢想同興趣都冇<br />\n人生好冇希望"},{"pid":"8a36650dc5e502f8cde74474eac97ef4f5d6132b","tid":338983,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"放鬆啲做囉 一緊張就好快攰<br />\n一攰做嘢好辛苦"},{"pid":"f35a2454ce03bf0f5ae182ecbc85173148b83e0c","tid":338983,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:27:43.000Z","msg":"每個人都有自己叻/做得比較得心應手既嘢<br />\n我唔信你無"},{"pid":"3f75ec63280016bf8f6e0ba5ec3cdc285af6028e","tid":338983,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9290cce392df99309f8c41a2f88352ddc00f7c","tid":338983,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中曬，已經覺得自己好努力，但係努力耐左都會心攰，心有餘而力不足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c819c3e17d2bad8108f3ef6b77d03e773ecb29","tid":338983,"uid":95413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:37:08.000Z","msg":"有同感   打緊份垃圾工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd1e9610d1a05b1ba47111bc025fdb093c98fcf","tid":338983,"uid":77663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:46:13.000Z","msg":"幾間u都唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 唯有出黎做野, 太多勁人老屎忽係上面壓住, 實力上又係初出茅廬之際,  俾人壓人工... 唉. 炒車炒到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb187a3f8d1508bf133ce94a3c467fbb324d1c66","tid":338983,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾間u都唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 唯有出黎做野, 太多勁人老屎忽係上面壓住, 實力上又係初出茅廬之際,  俾人壓人工... 唉. 炒車炒到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打返咩工"},{"pid":"7c07e9e46c1c27a8a465ff1723506dee4709c0ce","tid":338983,"uid":79128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:47:41.000Z","msg":"失敗者+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db81ce19a65db978bf1e744365971ae2792405ce","tid":338983,"uid":597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:52:19.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n其實我都係咁 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9d6af0fad26cbd7ed10a3614589583630de2e6","tid":338983,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日覺得自己好冇用，自問返工做野都幾用心，奈何唔醒目記性又差，所以做野好騰雞，又俾人話唔上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好灰心，但我真係有努力過，我覺得自己咩都做唔黎咁，無論係讀書定返工都係個失敗者，我有諗過係因為自己自卑先影響到工作能力，因為成日睇死自己做唔到，但係我又控制唔到咁諗，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁廢</blockquote><br />\nsame here<br />\n人到中年仲係一事冇成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇份長工做超過一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家失業中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d87599d82c1e4ddf6a69238b7ea6f24d47b4124","tid":338983,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中曬，已經覺得自己好努力，但係努力耐左都會心攰，心有餘而力不足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁先灰<br />\n明明付出既努力都唔少<br />\n返屋企都繼續庖書庖下行規<br />\n<br />\n但係一返到去做野<br />\n份工好似知道你弱點咁<br />\n又會咁啱問正啲唔熟既問題<br />\n屌又俾搞到人鬧<br />\n腦細對我既印象又差左<br />\n以為我懶<br />\n真係要講句屌你老母<br />\n但種灰法真係令人遞信辭工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c536959bd31ff02357247adc5d3dee286d2b7e2","tid":338983,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我成日覺得自己好冇用，自問返工做野都幾用心，奈何唔醒目記性又差，所以做野好騰雞，又俾人話唔上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好灰心，但我真係有努力過，我覺得自己咩都做唔黎咁，無論係讀書定返工都係個失敗者，我有諗過係因為自己自卑先影響到工作能力，因為成日睇死自己做唔到，但係我又控制唔到咁諗，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁廢</blockquote><br />\nsame here<br />\n人到中年仲係一事冇成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇份長工做超過一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家失業中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無一份過一年又誇左少少<br />\n有無認真諗下自己強項弱項係乜"},{"pid":"13ae9cfea30bf45f5e3de5bada659ea85d149a49","tid":338983,"uid":123170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:21:23.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似學咩都比人慢好多<br />\n又係唔醒目+冇記性<br />\n試過又係做收銀冇認d人個樣<br />\n結果找錯左d錯比第二個客<br />\n係咪覺得我仲冇用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae4541207738d2ff7112038e436b36653b28c50","tid":338983,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似學咩都比人慢好多<br />\n又係唔醒目+冇記性<br />\n試過又係做收銀冇認d人個樣<br />\n結果找錯左d錯比第二個客<br />\n係咪覺得我仲冇用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打少啲飞机"},{"pid":"8bd25cb14d033fa1b113082bcf3d2186b238ab78","tid":338983,"uid":123170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似學咩都比人慢好多<br />\n又係唔醒目+冇記性<br />\n試過又係做收銀冇認d人個樣<br />\n結果找錯左d錢比第二個客<br />\n係咪覺得我仲冇用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0b078ba8b762849e61f30206c6c60006fdb42562","tid":338983,"uid":77663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾間u都唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 唯有出黎做野, 太多勁人老屎忽係上面壓住, 實力上又係初出茅廬之際,  俾人壓人工... 唉. 炒車炒到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打返咩工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後期製作, 最廢既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225600516e3959cf917867c094af86c395306bd5","tid":338983,"uid":120719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:27:13.000Z","msg":"三十幾歲仲係揾得好少錢，好多人已經退休。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8936ba1322fb32d2eaff789a5eb963f5244c0b53","tid":338983,"uid":119379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:40:08.000Z","msg":"身同感受<br />\n<br />\n無辦法，勁又唔夠人勁，轉數又唔夠人快，自己以為已經出盡出力去做實掂啦，點知人地做出黎既野比自己更掂<br />\n<br />\n無架喇，但求有餐安樂餐飯食，平淡過埋下半世，同埋工作做好自己本份就算數<br />\n<br />\n我唔係天才呀，只係一個普通人"},{"pid":"4cf1a3f3f8f562d530def73919d63d5820aa7973","tid":338983,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:50:22.000Z","msg":"成日覺得身邊嘅人好叻好，自己就一無是處，點都追唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4277dacaf7e18039fa19cde982d6469675f0d09f","tid":338983,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日覺得自己好冇用，自問返工做野都幾用心，奈何唔醒目記性又差，所以做野好騰雞，又俾人話唔上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好灰心，但我真係有努力過，我覺得自己咩都做唔黎咁，無論係讀書定返工都係個失敗者，我有諗過係因為自己自卑先影響到工作能力，因為成日睇死自己做唔到，但係我又控制唔到咁諗，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁廢</blockquote><br />\n我都係，<br />\n容易緊張、手震、<br />\n精神差、成日冇乜體力咁。<br />\n(由細到大都係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n玩樂器好比心機日日練幾粒鐘，<br />\n但係出到黎既結果都係未如理想。"},{"pid":"4bcf3e95ee4374a04054288a91620f5f7d274283","tid":338983,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T20:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我成日覺得自己好冇用，自問返工做野都幾用心，奈何唔醒目記性又差，所以做野好騰雞，又俾人話唔上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好灰心，但我真係有努力過，我覺得自己咩都做唔黎咁，無論係讀書定返工都係個失敗者，我有諗過係因為自己自卑先影響到工作能力，因為成日睇死自己做唔到，但係我又控制唔到咁諗，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁廢</blockquote><br />\n我都係，<br />\n容易緊張、手震、<br />\n精神差、成日冇乜體力咁。<br />\n(由細到大都係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n玩樂器好比心機日日練幾粒鐘，<br />\n但係出到黎既結果都係未如理想。</blockquote>係唔係成日打J?"},{"pid":"d662184bb4b8f47dea64fabacd4cf732960ff49c","tid":338983,"uid":38648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T20:46:38.000Z","msg":"比下有餘, 但望上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6246dcf23aa94599e1bb86ad3eadbc5ea5b222","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩工咁大壓力</blockquote><br />\n見暑假咩工都去試下，去做收銀結果覺得壓力好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚找錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暑期工唔啱做咪走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係姐。。。只係覺得自己好無用。。。咩都做唔黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係做緊收銀,次次數錢都會check好多次,但都係覺得自己會錯，連數錢咁簡單都睇死自己，又試過check得太多次比個客屌</blockquote><br />\n我地要俾d信心自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b45d4066450b4b057400c6b0e9e536fabaf1f3","tid":338983,"uid":61829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"12ca31e67214b2e1a0eab6c9d9ad8ee4d8b79bdf","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前諗野好正面 最後被學業 現實 搞到好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書又唔叻 學歷又唔好 體能岩岩先起步操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要係自己連夢想同興趣都冇<br />\n人生好冇希望</blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前我都係好正面，覺得做唔黎代表我唔叻個樣姐，點知試得愈多範，樣樣都搞唔掂個陣就真係懷疑自己係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846b9eb6c3d2797386b5e7c6c438e10acd53684c","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放鬆啲做囉 一緊張就好快攰<br />\n一攰做嘢好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我成日都好緊張，太懷疑自己"},{"pid":"6f5fd1e4bd86d8a4cad2b3f080b84739b0d6f716","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個人都有自己叻/做得比較得心應手既嘢<br />\n我唔信你無</blockquote><br />\n應該有，但我未揾到"},{"pid":"9da2ecdcf5be5cf4950fd70de103de31f4af658c","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我成日覺得自己好冇用，自問返工做野都幾用心，奈何唔醒目記性又差，所以做野好騰雞，又俾人話唔上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好灰心，但我真係有努力過，我覺得自己咩都做唔黎咁，無論係讀書定返工都係個失敗者，我有諗過係因為自己自卑先影響到工作能力，因為成日睇死自己做唔到，但係我又控制唔到咁諗，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我要咁廢</blockquote><br />\n我都係，<br />\n容易緊張、手震、<br />\n精神差、成日冇乜體力咁。<br />\n(由細到大都係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n玩樂器好比心機日日練幾粒鐘，<br />\n但係出到黎既結果都係未如理想。</blockquote><br />\n容易緊張、手震*2"},{"pid":"8735e295e2d0a49e51c5cfa0cc2f6b77107cbcb9","tid":338983,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"好多巴絲同我一樣咁灰"}]}